    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="pr-lg-6 mb-3">
            <h5>Global Commerce</h5>
            <h1 class="title">Go global. Accept no compromise.</h1>
            <p class="mb-6">
              Establishing an international presence can be a challenge. Solidus allows you to sell to the world without diluting your brand.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get started</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-white" href="http://solidemo.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg">
          <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
            <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('use-cases/marketplace_hero@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('use-cases/marketplace_hero@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Global Commerce" >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="intro content-block--skewed content-block-gray-100 pb-0">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content-block pt-0">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="lead text-gray-600 text-center font-weight-light mb-4">
          Solidus powers the brands defining the future of eCommerce.
        </p>
        <%= partial "partials/community_logos" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="use-cases__image col-md">
          <img src="<%= image_path('use-cases/global-commerce_01_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('use-cases/global-commerce_01.svg') %>" class="img-fluid pr-md-2" alt="Integrations" width="100%" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="use-cases__header">
            <h5>Integrations</h5>
            <h2>Automate the pain out of international sales.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            With the right partners, unlocking new markets can become a matter of clicking a button. Solidus allows you to easily integrate with your service providers of choice, so that you don’t have to spend your day figuring out laws and regulations. Let the platform handle all the nitty gritty while you focus on servicing your new customers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content-block">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="use-cases__image col-md order-md-2">
            <img src="<%= image_path("use-cases/global-commerce_02@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("use-cases/global-commerce_02@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("use-cases/global-commerce_02@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Global commerce" />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md">
            <div class="use-cases__header">
              <h5>Global commerce</h5>
              <h2>Get as local as needed, but not more.</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
              It’s easy to choose the level of personalization that is just right for your brand. Solidus supports multiple languages and currencies, as well as per-country shipping methods, payment gateways and tax requirements. Get crazy and offer a local experience everywhere, or centralize your business to streamline your workflows and simplify operations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


