          Compliance is one of the biggest challenges for brands that want to go international. Solidus simplifies compliance implementations by providing a flexible architecture for meeting data and privacy regulations. Furthermore, because customer data is 100% owned by you, there are no third-party vendors to deal with.
        </p>
